OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776258665
OL,3,CFifth arrest made in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation after man dies
OL,6,FA fifth person has been arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of perverting the course of
OL,8,Fjustice in connection with a man's
OL,9,Fdeath in Kenilworth.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the address on
OL,12,FChesnut Avenue just before midnight on
OL,13,FFriday 20 March, after concerns were
OL,14,Fraised for the welfare of a man.
OL,16,FA man, 45 year old Carl Stephens was
OL,17,Ffound dead at the scene.
OL,19,FNow, a 51-year-old man from Solihull
OL,20,Fhas been bailed until June.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
