OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776258665
OL,3,CFifth arrest made in murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation after man dies
OL,6,FA 72-year-old woman previously
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of assisting an
OL,8,Foffender has also been bailed pending
OL,9,Ffurther enquiries.
OL,11,FThree people - a 24-year-old man from
OL,12,FBirmingham, a 49-year-old woman from
OL,13,FKenilworth and a 16-year-old boy from
OL,14,FKenilworth ` have been charged in
OL,15,Fconnection with his death.
OL,17,FThey are set to appear at Warwick
OL,18,FCrown Court on Wednesday 20 May 2026.
